---
title: One-Pot Double Chorizo & Tomato Penne with Hidden Veggies & Parmesan Cheese
description: Cheesy, rich and red, it’s a tomato sauce that’s very easy on the taste buds. There’s sweet and tender leek stirred through alongside mild chorizo, toss everything in a bowl of penne pasta and dinner just became irresistible.
